description: Democratic Governance: Strengthening the Human Rights Infrastructure in the Philippines

subproject.description: Progressive realization and implementation of the standards of human rights and institutionalization of reforms for democratic governance.  This “rights-reforms” approach is grounded locally where interventions are directed not only at the national level but also, more importantly, demonstrated at the level of LGUs and grassroots communities.
